---
---

<section class="services" id="servicios">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="section-label">Lo que hacemos</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Servicios diseñados para <em>hacer crecer</em> tu negocio</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="services-grid reveal">
    <!-- Service 01: Web Development — large featured card -->
    <div class="svc svc-1">
      <div>
        <div class="svc-num">01</div>
        <div class="svc-icon">🌐</div>
        <div class="svc-name">Desarrollo web</div>
        <div class="svc-desc">
          Creamos páginas web profesionales, rápidas y optimizadas que representan tu negocio y convierten visitas en clientes. Desde landings hasta tiendas online.
        </div>
        <div class="svc-tags">
          <span class="svc-tag">Landing pages</span>
          <span class="svc-tag">E-commerce</span>
          <span class="svc-tag">Web corporativa</span>
          <span class="svc-tag">Reservas online</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-arrow">↗</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 02: Social Media -->
    <div class="svc svc-2">
      <div class="svc-num svc-num-purple">02</div>
      <div class="svc-icon">📱</div>
      <div class="svc-name svc-name-dark">Gestión de redes sociales</div>
      <div class="svc-desc svc-desc-muted">
        Estrategia, contenido y publicación diaria. Construimos tu comunidad y posicionamos tu marca en Instagram y más.
      </div>
      <div class="svc-tags">
        <span class="svc-tag">Instagram</span>
        <span class="svc-tag">Contenido</span>
        <span class="svc-tag">Estrategia</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 03: Photography & Video -->
    <div class="svc svc-3">
      <div class="svc-num svc-num-green">03</div>
      <div class="svc-icon">📸</div>
      <div class="svc-name svc-name-dark">Foto y video profesional</div>
      <div class="svc-desc svc-desc-muted">
        Sesiones de fotografía de producto, negocio y reels para redes. Contenido visual que enamora a tus clientes.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 04: Automation -->
    <div class="svc svc-4">
      <div class="svc-num svc-num-faint">04</div>
      <div class="svc-icon">⚡</div>
      <div class="svc-name svc-name-sm">Automatización de procesos</div>
      <div class="svc-desc svc-desc-dark">
        Automatizamos tareas repetitivas: respuestas, pedidos, leads. Más tiempo para lo que importa.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 05: Strategy & Content -->
    <div class="svc svc-5">
      <div class="svc-num svc-num-faint">05</div>
      <div class="svc-icon">🎯</div>
      <div class="svc-name svc-name-sm">Estrategia & contenido</div>
      <div class="svc-desc svc-desc-dark">
        Planificamos y ejecutamos tu estrategia de contenido. Cada post con un propósito claro.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    padding: 120px 48px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .svc {
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 36px 32px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.25s;
  }

  .svc:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  /* Card variants */
  .svc-1 {
    background: var(--color-ink-soft);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    grid-row: span 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    min-height: 480px;
  }

  .svc-2 {
    background: var(--color-purple-light);
    min-height: 220px;
  }

  .svc-3 {
    background: var(--color-green-light);
    min-height: 220px;
  }

  .svc-4 {
    background: #1C1C1A;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    min-height: 220px;
  }

  .svc-5 {
    background: #161614;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    min-height: 220px;
  }

  /* Number variants */
  .svc-num {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    opacity: 0.4;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .svc-num-purple {
    color: var(--color-purple-deep);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .svc-num-green {
    color: var(--color-green-deep);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .svc-num-faint {
    opacity: 0.35;
  }

  /* Icon */
  .svc-icon {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* Name variants */
  .svc-name {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .svc-1 .svc-name {
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .svc-name-dark {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .svc-name-sm {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  /* Description variants */
  .svc-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
    opacity: 0.65;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .svc-desc-muted {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }

  .svc-desc-dark {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }

  /* Tags */
  .svc-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .svc-tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .svc-1 .svc-tag {
    background: rgba(247, 244, 239, 0.12);
    color: rgba(247, 244, 239, 0.7);
  }

  .svc-2 .svc-tag {
    background: rgba(123, 107, 176, 0.12);
    color: var(--color-purple-deep);
  }

  .svc-3 .svc-tag {
    background: rgba(90, 138, 82, 0.12);
    color: var(--color-green-deep);
  }

  /* Arrow */
  .svc-arrow {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 28px;
    right: 28px;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(247, 244, 239, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(247, 244, 239, 0.6);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .svc:hover .svc-arrow {
    background: rgba(247, 244, 239, 0.2);
    color: rgba(247, 244, 239, 0.9);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .svc-1 {
      grid-column: span 2;
      grid-row: span 1;
      min-height: 280px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .services {
      padding: 80px 24px;
    }

    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .svc-1 {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }
  }
</style>
